code: @SuppressWarnings("unchecked") protected <T> T invoke(MBeanServerConnection server, ObjectName name, String operationName) throws InstanceNotFoundException, MBeanException, ReflectionException, IOException {     return (T) server.invoke(name, operationName, null, null). }

@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") protected <T> T invoke(MBeanServerConnection server, ObjectName name, String operationName, Object[] params, String[] signature) throws InstanceNotFoundException, MBeanException, ReflectionException, IOException {     return (T) server.invoke(name, operationName, params, signature). }
